-- ds.h1: How to use?

The `how-it-works` component is capable of accepting `ftd` child components. 
You can see an example of this by checking the 
[how-it-works](index.html#how-it-works) on the homepage. It has `carousel` 
as child and `carousel` items as children. It can be used to add any other 
components as it's children. 

We recommend to close it with `-- end: how-it-works`, if it contains multiple 
children.

To use the `how-it-works` component you need to import `lib.ftd` inside your
`.ftd` file, as shown below:

